    Product description

    Wmszmsm Extra Long Cord Wired Headphone for TV

    • This is perfect for watching TV,great sound quality, and without disturbing others.
    • The long cable of 9.8FT/19.6FT facilitates moving and watching TV over long distances.
    • Headphones can adjust the volume for easy and convenient volume control.
    • Comfortable to wear, the cord is soft (not spring wire), and headphones adjustable in size and lightweight.
    • Not only suitable for TV, it is also compatible with other devices (computers/mobile phones/tablets) with 3.5mm jacks.

    Long Cord Wired Headphone

    40mm speaker with full sound, high, medium and low frequency balance

    Adjustable Volume

    The volume Is easily adjustable

    Memory Cotton Earmuffs

    Using memory cotton earmuffs with soft and skin friendly materials

    The Headhones are Extendable and Foldable

    Headband size adjustment and earphones can rotate 90 degrees

    Length(9.8IN/19.6IN)

    The long cable of 9.8FT/19.6FT facilitates moving

    Compatibility

    Suitable for use with 3.5mm jack

    (Note that there is no audio input and microphone function can only listen)

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
